room_title: Escape room "Through the Looking Glass" by Exit Strategy Escape Room in Cumberland
room_description: You  have  followed  the  white  rabbit  through  the  looking  glass,  now  he  is  gone  and  you  can't  get  back  without  his  7  magic  tokens  and pocket  watch!  The  looking  glass  disappears  in  1  hour,  can  you  find all of  the  tokens and  his  watch  to  get  back through in time?
